episodes.title: Woman Held Captive in a Cult for 30 Years | Good Morning Britain
episodes.description:
Katy Morgan-Davies was held captive in a cult ran by her father for 30 years before she managed to escape 5 years ago. She has shared her experiences in her book 'Caged Bird'.

episodes.title: Piers Morgan Calls Scientologists 'Gutless Cowards' In John Sweeney Interview | Good Morning Britain
episodes.description:
Subscribe now for more! http://bit.ly/1NbomQa
Broadcast on 11/10/2016
Piers Morgan calls scientologists 'gutless cowards' and 'sinister little weirdos' in a fascinating interview with John Sweeney, a journalist whose previous investigations into Scientology sparked harassment from the group.
